<div class="modal" id="pickModal"><h4 id="pickTitle">选择物品</h4><div class="pick-list" id="pickList"></div><div class="pick-cancel" onclick="closeModal()">取消</div></div>

<div class="container">
<div class="header"><h1>⚡ 绝区零 · 状态面板</h1><p>事件驱动刷新 &nbsp;·&nbsp; <span id="refreshBadge" style="color:var(--muted);font-size:11px">○ 等待事件</span></p></div>
